<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 28 Dec 2023 08:09:14 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>以色列国防军公布了周三在加沙战斗中丧生的三名以色列士兵的名字</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-28/ty-article/idf-names-three-israeli-soldiers-killed-in-gaza-fighting-on-wednesday/0000018c-af30-db94-afbd-af79141f0000</link><description>以色列军方还表示，加沙地带南部和中部还有其他士兵受重伤。</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Dec 2023 07:38:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-28/ty-article/idf-names-three-israeli-soldiers-killed-in-gaza-fighting-on-wednesday/0000018c-af30-db94-afbd-af79141f0000</guid></item><item><title>伊朗“独立”代理人的袭击增加了与以色列和美国发生直接冲突的可能性</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-28/ty-article/.premium/attacks-by-irans-independent-proxies-increase-odds-of-direct-clash-with-israel-and-u-s/0000018c-ad16-d22d-a3dd-bd7f52010000</link><description>自以色列与哈马斯战争爆发以来，德黑兰一直避免与以色列和美国直接对抗。但“抵抗轴心”成员所表现出的独立性使得伊斯兰共和国更难维持合理的推诿，并有可能将其拖入冲突</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Dec 2023 04:00:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-28/ty-article/.premium/attacks-by-irans-independent-proxies-increase-odds-of-direct-clash-with-israel-and-u-s/0000018c-ad16-d22d-a3dd-bd7f52010000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯大屠杀后，以色列极端正统派部长花了一天时间为地方选举进行政治活动</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-28/ty-article/.premium/haredi-israeli-minister-spent-day-after-hamas-massacre-politicking-for-local-election/0000018c-ace9-d22c-a98c-fced9a040000</link><description>当以色列陷入混乱时，梅厄·波鲁什正忙着做交易，以确保他的联合托拉犹太教党和他的儿子埃拉德市长以色列·波鲁什在即将到来的选举中的利益</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Dec 2023 04:00:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-28/ty-article/.premium/haredi-israeli-minister-spent-day-after-hamas-massacre-politicking-for-local-election/0000018c-ace9-d22c-a98c-fced9a040000</guid></item><item><title>三名士兵在加沙丧生；自杀式无人机摧毁戈兰高地的建筑物</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-28/ty-article-live/suicide-drone-hits-buildings-on-golan-israel-on-very-high-alert-on-lebanon-border/0000018c-ae77-db94-afbd-ae7f8d860000</link><description>以色列国防军表示在加沙城发现了更多隧道 ■ 自杀式无人机损坏了戈兰高地的建筑物 ■ 以色列国防军公布了在加沙战斗中丧生的三名士兵的名字 ■ 巴勒斯坦人：六人在西岸无人机袭击中丧生 ■ 美国对国际原子能机构关于伊朗铀产量增加的报告“非常关注”浓缩 ■ 以色列军队解散定居者部队的五名士兵 ■ 以色列军队深化在汗尤尼斯的地面行动 ■ 自10 月7 日以来，以色列境内至少有1,300 名平民和士兵被杀；加沙至少有 130 名人质被扣押 ■ 哈马斯卫生部：加沙有 21,110 人死亡、55,243 人受伤</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Dec 2023 03:39:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-28/ty-article-live/suicide-drone-hits-buildings-on-golan-israel-on-very-high-alert-on-lebanon-border/0000018c-ae77-db94-afbd-ae7f8d860000</guid></item><item><title>以色列副总检察长表示，本-格维尔部非法发放了 14,000 张枪支许可证</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-27/ty-article/.premium/ben-gvirs-ministry-distributed-14-000-gun-licenses-illegally-israels-deputy-ag-says/0000018c-acea-d45c-a98e-afeef7530000</link><description>本-格维尔的国家安全部利用加沙战争来发挥“创意”，规避有关枪支许可证和所有权的现有法规。司法部认为违法后将其关闭</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Dec 2023 21:46:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-27/ty-article/.premium/ben-gvirs-ministry-distributed-14-000-gun-licenses-illegally-israels-deputy-ag-says/0000018c-acea-d45c-a98e-afeef7530000</guid></item><item><title>五名以色列士兵因在约旦河西岸袭击巴勒斯坦人而被定居者活动单位解雇</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-27/ty-article/.premium/five-soldiers-dismissed-from-idf-from-settler-activist-unit-for-assaulting-palestinians/0000018c-ac4b-d22c-a98c-fc6fea220000</link><description>根据巴勒斯坦人的证词，袭击者剥光他们的衣服并殴打他们，在他们身上撒尿，并在他们身上熄灭香烟。以色列国防军最近停止了该部队的行动活动，该部队从西岸前哨基地招募定居青年服兵役</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Dec 2023 21:43:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-27/ty-article/.premium/five-soldiers-dismissed-from-idf-from-settler-activist-unit-for-assaulting-palestinians/0000018c-ac4b-d22c-a98c-fc6fea220000</guid></item><item><title>据报道，加沙辛贝特消息来源警告哈马斯将于 10 月初对以色列发动重大袭击</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-27/ty-article/shin-bet-source-in-gaza-reportedly-warned-of-major-hamas-attack-in-early-october/0000018c-acab-d22c-a98c-fcefb17e0000</link><description>据12频道报道，消息来源的负责人将这一信息进行了传递，但最终只停留在较低级别，没有到达更高级别的当局。辛贝特对此回应称，“所有现有信息都将受到审查”</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Dec 2023 19:28:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-27/ty-article/shin-bet-source-in-gaza-reportedly-warned-of-major-hamas-attack-in-early-october/0000018c-acab-d22c-a98c-fcefb17e0000</guid></item><item><title>报告：以色列高等法院法官准备废除去年夏天通过的关键司法政变法</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-27/ty-article/report-high-court-justices-poised-to-nullify-key-judicial-coup-law-passed-last-summer/0000018c-ac99-d22d-a3dd-bdf985e20000</link><description>报告称，15 名法官中有 8 名支持废除该法律，该法律取消了法院对政府决定进行司法审查的能力。最终裁决将在未来几周内公布。以色列司法当局拒绝“承认”“未经证实的泄密”</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Dec 2023 19:20:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-27/ty-article/report-high-court-justices-poised-to-nullify-key-judicial-coup-law-passed-last-summer/0000018c-ac99-d22d-a3dd-bdf985e20000</guid></item><item><title>甘茨反击本格维尔，但表示他将继续留在以色列紧急政府“以赢得战争”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-27/ty-article/gantz-pushes-back-against-ben-gvir-says-hell-remain-in-emergency-govt-to-win-war/0000018c-ac5c-d22c-a98c-fc7c07010000</link><description>极右翼部长伊塔马尔·本-格维尔决定不延长以色列监狱管理局专员的任期，这违反了甘茨政党与利库德集团在 10 月 7 日战争开始后进入紧急政府的协议</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Dec 2023 18:36:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-27/ty-article/gantz-pushes-back-against-ben-gvir-says-hell-remain-in-emergency-govt-to-win-war/0000018c-ac5c-d22c-a98c-fc7c07010000</guid></item><item><title>开枪赋予了我力量。携带一个是我在以色列感觉最不安全的</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2023-12-27/ty-article/.highlight/shooting-a-gun-empowered-me-carrying-one-is-the-least-safe-ive-felt-in-israel/0000018c-ac0f-d462-afbe-accf685a0000</link><description>我只是希望数以万计新获得许可的以色列枪支拥有者——无论是否经过授权方批准——都知道他们刚刚购买的武器的重量，并对这种力量保持敬畏和恐惧</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Dec 2023 17:44:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2023-12-27/ty-article/.highlight/shooting-a-gun-empowered-me-carrying-one-is-the-least-safe-ive-felt-in-israel/0000018c-ac0f-d462-afbe-accf685a0000</guid></item><item><title>“加沙死亡现在在以色列是一个禁忌话题”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2023-12-27/ty-article-podcast/death-in-gaza-is-a-taboo-subject-in-israel-right-now/0000018c-aaec-d885-abdf-feeec86a0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Dec 2023 17:05:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2023-12-27/ty-article-podcast/death-in-gaza-is-a-taboo-subject-in-israel-right-now/0000018c-aaec-d885-abdf-feeec86a0000</guid></item><item><title>加沙眼中的加沙战争：阅读《国土报》关于难以想象的现实的重要文章</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2023-12-27/ty-article-timeline/.premium/war-in-gaza-though-gazan-eyes-read-the-best-haaretz-articles-from-an-unthinkable-reality/0000018c-abf1-d22d-a3dd-bff9a4b20000</link><description></description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Dec 2023 16:34:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2023-12-27/ty-article-timeline/.premium/war-in-gaza-though-gazan-eyes-read-the-best-haaretz-articles-from-an-unthinkable-reality/0000018c-abf1-d22d-a3dd-bff9a4b20000</guid></item><item><title>黎巴嫩裔澳大利亚人、他的妻子和真主党成员兄弟在以色列空袭中丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2023-12-27/ty-article/lebanese-australian-his-wife-and-hezbollah-member-brother-killed-in-israeli-airstrike/0000018c-ac06-d22d-a3dd-bd7f8f280000</link><description>据报道，这次空袭发生在以色列和真主党之间最近在黎巴嫩边境爆发敌对行动之际。澳大利亚外交部表示已获悉该报道并正在寻求证实</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Dec 2023 16:30:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2023-12-27/ty-article/lebanese-australian-his-wife-and-hezbollah-member-brother-killed-in-israeli-airstrike/0000018c-ac06-d22d-a3dd-bd7f8f280000</guid></item><item><title>土耳其领导人称以色列总理“与希特勒没有什么不同”后，埃尔多安和内塔尼亚胡互斥</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-27/ty-article/erdogan-netanyahu-trade-barbs-after-turkey-leader-compares-israeli-pm-to-hitler/0000018c-abcf-d45c-a98e-abcf6fcd0000</link><description>“内塔尼亚胡所做的事情比希特勒所做的事情还少吗？”事实并非如此，”埃尔多安说。内塔尼亚胡回应称，埃尔多安应该是最后一个对以色列说教的人，称他正在对库尔德人实施种族灭绝，并保持着监禁记者的世界纪录</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Dec 2023 15:50:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-27/ty-article/erdogan-netanyahu-trade-barbs-after-turkey-leader-compares-israeli-pm-to-hitler/0000018c-abcf-d45c-a98e-abcf6fcd0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队无人机袭击约旦河西岸难民营，造成六名巴勒斯坦人死亡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-27/ty-article/.premium/six-palestinians-killed-in-israeli-army-drone-attack-on-west-bank-refugee-camp/0000018c-ab8e-d22d-a3dd-bfff58b40000</link><description>以色列国防军表示，这六人是一群恐怖分子，他们一直向在该地区活动的部队投掷爆炸装置。近几个月来，以色列军队加强了在约旦河西岸巴勒斯坦城市图尔卡尔姆附近努尔沙姆斯难民营的行动</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Dec 2023 15:46:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-27/ty-article/.premium/six-palestinians-killed-in-israeli-army-drone-attack-on-west-bank-refugee-camp/0000018c-ab8e-d22d-a3dd-bfff58b40000</guid></item><item><title>12 个议程设置《国土报》播客剧集讲述 2023 年的故事</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-27/ty-article-timeline/.premium/12-agenda-setting-haaretz-podcast-episodes-that-tell-the-story-of-2023/0000018c-a56a-d97c-a9ec-bfefa18b0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Dec 2023 15:26:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-27/ty-article-timeline/.premium/12-agenda-setting-haaretz-podcast-episodes-that-tell-the-story-of-2023/0000018c-a56a-d97c-a9ec-bfefa18b0000</guid></item><item><title>伊朗革命卫队：10月7日以色列发生的袭击是对卡西姆·苏莱马尼遇刺事件的回应</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2023-12-27/ty-article/.premium/irans-revolutionary-guard-oct-7-attack-was-in-response-to-soleimani-assassination/0000018c-abb7-d044-a5fd-ebbf050b0000</link><description>哈马斯很快否认了伊朗革命卫队的说法，这表明它参与策划了 10 月 7 日对以色列南部的袭击</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Dec 2023 15:20:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2023-12-27/ty-article/.premium/irans-revolutionary-guard-oct-7-attack-was-in-response-to-soleimani-assassination/0000018c-abb7-d044-a5fd-ebbf050b0000</guid></item><item><title>第一位以色列依良心拒服加沙战争者被判入狱：“我知道这是正确的事情”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-27/ty-article-magazine/.premium/first-israeli-conscientious-objector-of-gaza-war-is-jailed-im-doing-the-right-thing/0000018c-ab74-d885-abdf-ff7e09890000</link><description>18 岁的塔尔·米特尼克周二拒绝应征入伍，目前正在军事监狱服刑 30 天。他在宣判前夕表示，政府希望“加深占领并不允许任何形式的异议”</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Dec 2023 15:19:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-27/ty-article-magazine/.premium/first-israeli-conscientious-objector-of-gaza-war-is-jailed-im-doing-the-right-thing/0000018c-ab74-d885-abdf-ff7e09890000</guid></item><item><title>在哈马斯袭击前不久，这个警告就出现了。帕加前哨发生了什么？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-27/ty-article-magazine/.premium/shortly-before-the-hamas-attack-this-warning-arrived-what-happened-at-the-paga-outpost/0000018c-a631-dc33-a78c-bfb9f5360000</link><description>R. 正在前往检查是否有渗透嫌疑的途中，却被禁止靠近围栏。两小时后，哈马斯开始发起进攻 ■ 少数士兵阻止了数十名试图占领纳哈尔奥兹基布兹附近军事哨所的恐怖分子。十二名士兵被杀，他们的父母想要答案</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Dec 2023 15:00:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-27/ty-article-magazine/.premium/shortly-before-the-hamas-attack-this-warning-arrived-what-happened-at-the-paga-outpost/0000018c-a631-dc33-a78c-bfb9f5360000</guid></item><item><title>以色列面临的真正危险先于哈马斯袭击 — — 并且仍然是最大的威胁</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-27/ty-article/.premium/real-danger-facing-israel-precedes-hamas-attack-and-remains-biggest-threat/0000018c-ab1b-d885-abdf-ff5f75ce0000</link><description>去年出去抗议的数十万以色列人乐观地认为，内塔尼亚胡的司法政变已经随着他的支持率下降而消退。但制度和社会的衰退在最近几个月才加速，一些人已经付出了代价</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Dec 2023 14:58:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-27/ty-article/.premium/real-danger-facing-israel-precedes-hamas-attack-and-remains-biggest-threat/0000018c-ab1b-d885-abdf-ff5f75ce0000</guid></item></channel></rss>